      <title>熟络</title>
      <link href="2018/02/11/%E7%86%9F%E7%BB%9C/"/>
      <url>2018/02/11/%E7%86%9F%E7%BB%9C/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>​    她室友结婚当天，我们在参加的时候，私下里，微信上不停地聊天，商量着怎么抢红包，笑死。更逗的是，婚礼上相互偷拍，黑照一堆。</p><p>​    后来，她的室友先收到了我的黑照，我还被威胁了…….</p><p>​    那个时候，聊天互损，过了没几天，她的室友说：<img src="/2018/02/11/%E7%86%9F%E7%BB%9C/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20210417163914.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/2018/02/11/%E7%86%9F%E7%BB%9C/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20210417163914.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="emmm"></p>]]></content>
      
      
